Package author: Mikhail S. Dubrovin

Brief description:
==================

After 2016-11-14 mtg of Chris with AMO/SXR people
Daniel Jeremy Higley <dhigley@stanford.edu>
come up with idea of GUI-based approach for SXR monitoring tools. 
This package contains a few modules with implementation of this tool.

